{"tid":1383767,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"非常時期，希望連仔可以為反送中多開幾個分台","createTime":"2019-07-29T18:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T00:49:17.000Z","uid":270111,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ccf4e15db65b7ec825b2adbd8627f3329e891a","tid":1383767,"uid":270111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"比返credit原案巴打先<br />\n<br />\n[緊急!!] 強烈建議連仔時事台加開分台<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dshynT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dshynT</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中呢排幾乎所有既post都放晒係時事台，而有時候大家d post既內容都係相近，又或者討論緊同一個方向既野，結果開左好多個相似既post，令到一d重要既post反而沉左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如721元朗恐襲同中環36槍事件不停同時推，推下推下甚至會有互屌既情況出現，冇話邊樣比邊樣重要，但係無可避免會造成混亂。<br />\n<br />\n連登雖然冇香討同bk d會員咁熱衷反送中，但係都有唔少人因為反送中而開始mon連登甚至開ac（例如小弟），將唔同既post分門別類可以令巴絲討論更加有效率。<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟建議可以開個反送中既catagory，然後係下面再開幾個分台。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">情報台：</span><br />\n已fact check，官方正式資訊（例如記者會時間、中共強烈譴責），活動預告（不過唔好開太多po講同一個event）同埋即時戰況（狗隻佈陣調動、地鐵站伏兵）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣台：</span><br />\n希望煲大既情報資訊，同埋文宣手足整完都可以放上黎校對下，校對完再射去其他台度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">戰略台：</span><br />\n討論前線戰略（應攻應守、如何流水進退等），政局大方向（以中聯辦為目標等），裝備同奇謀（丟雞蛋，丁權訴訟）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">救命台：</span><br />\n極緊急既情報，或者未必fact check到既，例如有人留底左遺言失左蹤，有group爆義士個人資料，後生仔冇錢食飯點資助等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">反送中吹水台：</span><br />\n讚下好人好事，比人放下負，罵下黑警，J下若驊，又或者其他分唔到類既po 。<br />\n<br />\n希望其他巴絲比d意見，覺得應該搞既麻煩推到比連仔睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597a8ba8d6a41a5c39be8a8e872ad713219e12ab","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:29:30.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"e6dd1151c9f8bce30cb7a929fa87fd1d09466db4","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:29:54.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"c0119cbaf8bcaf4e19baf283c914664b539a4502","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"e2570b30aa554c786aa4c3363c75a985ba0d8668","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:30:32.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"9cce5d1e6659550a1ebfd1041bfed17213796aef","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:30:47.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"0b8f7d17fc5a1cbf1f0806fd19ed98aa2b441999","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:31:01.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"24bb7b43a7fc90acb7f6c16ec2ee36de3c68a615","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"1d9bd6a9e1b773183bb4bfa471b2ab75a0c76e25","tid":1383767,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fad0cac66f99836350b88c3ecb3f4d3dda77f17","tid":1383767,"uid":102801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:31:22.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"8ab58a302e6ed829b0a6603d69286b5942623294","tid":1383767,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50c80cbeffc20a90f410c4f3c35e9a5a1c5ca074","tid":1383767,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20fd4937f29b5fc4f8ddd16c0bed61c5e34a2b2","tid":1383767,"uid":276215,"like":1,"di